privateJob.title: Bajaj finserv Executive Recruitment 2021   Apply online for  Vacancies in Trichy
privateJob.body:
Name of the Vacancies:

  •  Area Manager

Description:

A new private job vacancy from Bajaj finserv has been published in Trichy for the post of Area Manager. If you are looking for a job in Trichy, then this is an opportunity for you, you must have relevant skills to apply for these Vacancies in Trichy. If you are interested in these posts which have come out in Trichy, then check the details below, which include Roles and Responsibility, Key Skills, Documents Required, etc.

Total vacancies:

  • Various vacancies have released.

Selection Process:

  •  Handwritten test

Role and responsibility:

  • Duties and Responsibilities
  • Relationship Management with existing CD / Digital Manufacturer.
  • Engage with manufacturers to build and strengthen relationships.
  • Design and execute promotion schemes with the manufacturer.
  • Conceptualize and develop marketing plans for the products in line with the business plan.

Application fee:

  • No information is given about the application required.

Educational qualification:

The candidates who are interested to apply for Bajaj finserv job must have the following qualification:

  • The candidates must have completed the Graduation from a recognized university to apply for the application Bajaj finserv Executive Recruitment 2021

Key skills required :

The candidates who are interested to apply in these job openings must have the following key skills that are required to do this:

  • People Management skills.
  • Demonstrated success & achievement orientation.
  • Excellent communication skills.
  • Strong bias for action & driving results in a high-performance environment.
  • Excellent relationship skills.
  • Affirmative.

Bajaj finserv Area Manager PayScale :

  • The Payscale information will be decided at the time of the interview.

The document needs to be carried:

The candidates who will be selected for the interview must carry the below-mentioned documents:

  • The first and foremost thing is your resume/CV which has your educational background and other related information.
  • You must have your Adhaar card for identity purposes.
  • You must have other identity proofs like a PAN card, voter id, or Passport to prove your citizenship.
  • At last, you should have photocopies of important educational certificates.

How to apply for Bajaj finserv Executive Recruitment 2021?

Candidates who are eligible and interested to apply for Bajaj finserv Job then you should follow the below steps to apply:

Note: You can also apply by clicking the apply now button shown above to apply directly from here

  • First of all, read the Bajaj finserv Executive Recruitment 2021 notification thoroughly at the official website @Bajaj finserv.com
  • You should have an email id and a phone number for communication purposes.
  • Click on the apply now link for the post you want to apply for.
  • Fill in the required details and submit.
  • Pay the application fee asked for.
  • Finally submit and download the application form for future purposes.
